<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comments Application</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="container">
        <h1>Programming Career journey</h1>
        <p>This is the platform to share about which programming you love and that landed your first job</p>
        <ul>
            <% for(let com of comments) {%>
              <li><strong> Created By: <%=com.name%></strong><br> <strong>Topic:</strong>  <%=com.topic%> <br> <strong>Comment:</strong>  <br> <%=com.comment%></li>   
           <%}%>
        </ul>
        <a href="/new">Add a new comment</a>
    </header>
    <footer>
        <p>Created by: Justice Sithole</p> 
        <p>I used nodejs, express and mongodb and a template called ejs for my front end</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>